IN -- HE WAS TAKEN BACK TO THE

00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:25.840
POLICE STATION AND THEY FOUND

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:26.110
THE TEACHER'S I.D. AND WOMEN'S

00:01:26.110 --> 00:01:26.970
UNDERWEAR.

