I ASKED IF THERE WAS

00:01:29.780 --> 00:01:30.040
ANYTHING DANGEROUS IN THE

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:33.750
BACKPACK.

00:01:33.750 --> 00:01:36.680
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:39.690
HE SAID YES.

